				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "0f990855-3b33-4898-8616-b9a17bc83092")
	)
	(text "4.2 Power Path Management\nLTC4412 Ideal Diode Controller\nAutomatically selects active power source\nPrevents reverse current\nEnsures seamless switching between battery types"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 510.54 311.15 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "12a709e4-7008-4174-8c32-654a98e9b803")
	)
	(text "7. Solar Charging System\nCN3165 Solar Charge Controller\nHandles LiPo charging from solar panel\nEfficient energy harvesting\nSupports autonomous field deployment"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 650.24 410.21 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "14fdcd36-622c-4192-8e54-e936d50cc1b8")
	)
	(text "1. Overview\n\nThis design is a production-optimized modification of the open-source nRF9151 Feather platform, tailored for animal tracking applications.\n\nThe system integrates:\n\nCellular (NTN/LTE-M/NB-IoT) + GPS via nRF9151\nLoRa communication via SX1262\nDual battery support (LiPo + Solar OR LiSOCl₂)\nUltra-low power operation\nCompact form factor (≤ 50.8mm × 22.86mm)\n\nAll development-board-specific and non-essential components have been removed to improve cost, efficiency, and manufacturability."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 513.08 52.07 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "371e45ae-bbb3-42a0-89ab-c549b1faa8b1")
	)
	(text "SOLAR PANEL CONNECTOR LIPO 1 WATT"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 76.2 166.37 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.2446 1.2446)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "40f063fc-ff69-4f27-80d8-63c897bbb089")
	)
	(text "LORA_SX1262"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 334.01 577.85 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "4e827044-dcda-4aae-b6e8-b521d8576bdb")
	)
	(text "BATTERY CONNECTOR CHARGING(3.7V-4.2V)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 226.06 78.74 90)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.2446 1.2446)
			)
			(justify right top)
		)
		(uuid "6d151106-a4b0-49e6-9ed5-d1b3bfa43225")
	)
	(text "3. Core Functional Blocks\n3.1 Main Processing Unit\nnRF9151 SiP\nIntegrated LTE-M / NB-IoT / NTN modem\nIntegrated GPS\nMain MCU for system control\nInterfaces with LoRa module and power control logic"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 511.81 173.99 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "7a953240-54d0-4a76-9345-fc69d19126f4")
	)
	(text "POWER PATH MANAGER FOR BATTERIES"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 236.22 198.12 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "7d63f907-e47d-4998-a0e5-e2b999383fde")
	)
	(text "4.3 Voltage Regulation Strategy\n\nInstead of a PMIC (e.g., nPM1300), the design uses:\n\nTwo buck regulators (Master + Slave)\nControlled using RC timing + PGOOD logic\nEliminates need for external microcontroller for sequencing\n5. Power Sequencing (Critical Design)\n\nThe system uses RC-based timing (“power inertia”) to meet nRF9151 strict requirements:\n\nVDD (core) must power ON first and OFF last\nVDD_GPIO must power OFF first\n\n5.1 Master Rail (Main 3.3V – Core Supply)\n\nComponents:\n\n100kΩ resistor\n10µF capacitor\n\nBehavior:\n\nStartup delay: ~700ms\nShutdown delay: ~1000ms\n\nPurpose:\n\nProvides stable core voltage\nAllows:\nLTE modem network detach\nSafe flash memory writes\nSystem state preservation\n5.2 Slave Rail (GPIO Supply – Fast Rail)\n\nComponents:\n\n100kΩ pull-down\n10nF capacitor\n\nBehavior:\n\nStartup: activates after master reaches ~95%\nShutdown: discharges in ~1ms\n\nPurpose:\n\nEnsures GPIO power drops before core power\nPrevents back-powering through I/O pins\nProtects nRF9151 integrity"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 651.51 148.59 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "843df7af-4037-47da-b349-dcf1f371c2ea")
	)
	(text "SIMCARD_SLOT"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 49.53 266.7 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "94a899b0-aee9-44e8-912f-c8ce7125fba9")
	)
	(text "GILBERTO_VERSION NRF9151 _SX1262 LORA"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 999.49 228.6 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.2446 1.2446)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "9a4f9432-c76d-4e9e-a7c2-051cb0b6c564")
	)
	(text "GILBERTO_VERSION NRF9151 _SX1262 LORA"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 453.644 36.83 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 9.4488 9.4488)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "9aa735b0-7521-455e-97c1-ca65034383d1")
	)
	(text "4. Power Architecture\n4.1 Dual Battery Support\n\nThe system supports two mutually exclusive power configurations:\n\nLiPo Battery (Rechargeable)\nCharged via solar input\nManaged by CN3165 solar charge controller\nLiSOCl₂ Battery (Primary)\nNon-rechargeable\nUsed for ultra-long-life deployments"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 511.81 251.46 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "9c894d0e-a263-408b-9d7b-5274e9df5b36")
	)
	(text "JTAG HEADER"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 133.35 518.16 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "a2365ca5-2865-4f8c-b5d3-1928fb930176")
	)
	(text "2. Removed Components\n\nThe following features from the original Feather design are excluded:\n\nRP2040 co-processor\nUSB-C interface\nExternal NOR Flash (Winbond 4MB)\nNon-essential push buttons (only Reset retained)\nQWIIC connector"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 513.08 124.46 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3.1496 3.1496)
			)
			(justify left top)
